    <br><br /><br><br /><br><br /><br><br /><br>
    <p>September may mean back to class for most, but that doesn&rsquo;t necessarily mean for reading, writing, science or math! Keenobby.com connects people to share in authentic arts, crafts, fashion, beauty, cooking, and baking experiences in New York City. Their website hosts a global community of &ldquo;makers&rdquo; showcasing creative talents through various classes. The site&rsquo;s visitors can then connect with the &ldquo;makers&rdquo; and select join in on their classes, which are hosted at various locations and times. Experiences are broken down into four different categories: Arts &amp; Crafts, Food &amp; Drink, Health &amp; Wellness, and Nature &amp; Science.</p>
